data.description: Price reduced!!! Seller motivated! Beautiful 2 story home with 3 BR, 2.5 BA in Silverado Ranch area. Laminated flooring in first floor, stainless steel kitchen appliances included. New water heater installed only last month. R.O system in place! Primary BR has balcony. Full size driveway and community parking is just a few steps away. Low monthly HOA! Community has 2 pools, a playground and a dog run.
